From: Chris Wilson <chris@chris-wilson.co.uk>
Date: Thu, 14 Dec 2017 12:26:13 +0000
Subject: drm/i915: Show engine state when hangcheck detects a stall
Git-commit: 84ef3a727e32ac32380e28198c3fdc6dcf941ec6
Patch-mainline: v4.16-rc1
References: FATE#326289 FATE#326079 FATE#326049 FATE#322398 FATE#326166

Knowing the state of the engine when hangcheck thinks it is stalling is
useful for both debugging hangcheck itself and the potential cause of an
unwanted stall.

